{"tid":2267644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【叫雞群組】疑內地妓女確診 4警員「密切接觸」需隔離","createTime":"2020-11-02T08:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:51:31.000Z","uid":222970,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"156c928028896cb0a0b98737a4f61bde0b89ebf0","tid":2267644,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahtfrnf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fahtfrnf.png&h=82b59bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【妓女群組】疑內地妓女確診 4警員密切接觸需隔離<br />\n<br />\nHealth Concept Editorial<br />\n2020年11月2日 11:22<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情反覆，衞生防護中心昨日(1日)公布的一宗本地不明源頭個案，涉及一名42歲等待遣返的中國籍女子。據了解該名女子於警方上周三一次掃黃行動中，被發現沒有合法居留權，被將其帶返旺角警署，故患者懷疑是性工作者。事件中有23名警務人員曾與她接觸，4警員被列為<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>密切接觸者</strong></span></span>需要接受隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n10月28日警方曾聯同入境處職員，於旺角塘尾道206號東方泛達酒店進行掃黃行動，其中發現上述確診女子沒有合法居留權，將其帶返旺角警署，之後轉到青山灣入境事務中心，短暫逗留再轉往馬頭角羈留中心，她上周五 (30日) 發病後確診。警方指出，確診女子在10月28日至30日被羈留於旺角警署，有23名警務人員曾與她接觸，其中4人被列為密切接觸者需要接受隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，該女子於今年8月18日由珠海乘船非法入境本港，至今約兩個半月。警方指出，拘捕行動中警務人員並沒有跟患者有任何放蛇接觸，拘捕過程中亦一直有採取保護措施。行動中，人員拘捕6名年齡介乎24歲至42歲內地女子，涉嫌非法入境，於單位內檢獲一批避孕套、潤滑劑及毛巾等。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君則表示指出，暫未肯定該名女子何時到港，她報稱到港後一直住於酒店，沒有外出。<br />\n<br />\n消息來源：衞生防護中心、警務處"},{"pid":"d646e81ca3509e38f389191f8fa5eda659649fd9","tid":2267644,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"黑警叫雞唔俾錢已經唔係第一次嘅事！<br />\n<br />\n警員邱樹明 疑似叫雞唔俾錢 毆打妓女及恐嚇?????????<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXV16o7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXV16o7.jpg&h=bcbaf873&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qDnQQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qDnQQO.jpg&h=58d612e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c6fd51588bc297d4ed582b88a53572565fd4fea","tid":2267644,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f55450dcf3225e6a9568287031951349ae7b1a54","tid":2267644,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:29:43.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"93ce7463e12081f5e1c461e971992ca223a1276c","tid":2267644,"uid":173326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"冇俾錢就唔叫叫雞"},{"pid":"8b566dc8391e57b8154c6dcd2c900332d100b86e","tid":2267644,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c855dff39e6c3cea8e80725481f4867c97c4e22","tid":2267644,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"叫老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ce90f68f23a48684c8fc43b3feb5cae44ba2fa","tid":2267644,"uid":335783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0c0cd9bdb00a2e7af0eeb729540ad1b47fc6ab","tid":2267644,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"疫情過左咁耐，咁多人中左武肺都唔會認自己叫雞<br />\n第一個認叫雞既居然係d狗<br />\n係咪on9"},{"pid":"5cf6c862b2d18e8c5ac3389737fb6aa00c138c74","tid":2267644,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"賤賊冇女溝，要叫雞先有閪屌好出奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5afed62bae30e8bc99c1a01eecaf77c7073c0